{"tid":1196934,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"成日話我地和理非無用, 咁我想問你地勇武派尋日又做左d咩成績出黎?","createTime":"2019-06-10T00:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T02:42:30.000Z","uid":79481,"like":7,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3a8b2b9067a04bf4b3db919bf37980c594a75117","tid":1196934,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:41:57.000Z","msg":"我知講事實一定無人岩聽<br />\n<br />\n但我尋晚睇直播淨係見到一堆無組織<br />\n<br />\n淨係識玩下鐵馬<br />\n<br />\n黑警拎警棍推前<br />\n<br />\n成班友就好似小學雞玩捉咁四散走佬<br />\n<br />\n然後望住真勇武果d一個一個俾黑警拉入佢地防線到留案底<br />\n<br />\n最後都係乜野成績都做唔到出黎 乜都爭取唔到<br />\n<br />\n真係睇到人好老尷 好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f6f1f91d72c9bd5f3ec2a3e4f47a374aba3e4d","tid":1196934,"uid":220245,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:42:42.000Z","msg":"我立刻屌你老母"},{"pid":"889fa0afa83e0bfe77cbc95cda00b4e34873c0de","tid":1196934,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我立刻屌你老母</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1576452809f0b742bf9b321577e4b9022867a59a","tid":1196934,"uid":229425,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:45:03.000Z","msg":"如果琴日果一百萬人全部都係勇武派，<br />\n結果會點？"},{"pid":"9de3981649aa4866de1e70b256201dbaa162c074","tid":1196934,"uid":79481,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05f6f1f91d72c9bd5f3ec2a3e4f47a374aba3e4d","tid":1196934,"uid":220245,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:42:42.000Z","msg":"我立刻屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:45:15.000Z","msg":"淨係識人身攻擊<br />\n<br />\n低質回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85066f58fdfe850d86c9a99a9f2e994c12d0c779","tid":1196934,"uid":79481,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1576452809f0b742bf9b321577e4b9022867a59a","tid":1196934,"uid":229425,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:45:03.000Z","msg":"如果琴日果一百萬人全部都係勇武派，<